<dl id="n26071k"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n26" href="#n26071k">N26 (VI.B.18)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n26all.htm#n26071k"> 71(k)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Caer leon </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Caerleon <font color="green">[Welsh: city or fort of the legion]</font> is a small Welsh town beside the River Usk, a few miles north of Newport. Tradition has it that after the Romans left Britain, Arthur set up his court there. </mm> </dd></dl>
